Sierra Nevada forest fire. 
</P>
<P>
 An undetermined number of people staying around the recreational lake were 
ordered to leave at midafternoon as a precaution because of fears the fire 
might reach the lake, said Sierra National Forest spokeswoman Robyn Smith. 
</P>
<P>
 Nearly 400 residents of Big Creek west of the lake were evacuated Thursday as 
