<HEADLINE>
<P>
ABC WILL SHOW FINAL GAME LIVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 At the request of affiliate KABC in Los Angeles, ABC Sports will show the 
Little League World Series final today between Northridge and Venezuela live in 
the L.A. area. 
</P>
<P>
 Coverage will begin at 12:30 p.m. PDT. 
</P>
<P>
 The game originally was scheduled to be shown live in the East and on a 
tape-delayed basis in the West. It still will be shown on a tape-delayed basis 
in other parts of the Pacific time zone. 
</P>
