<HEADLINE>
<P>
IT'S TIME FOR RAMS TO DROP BACK AND PUNT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mid '70s: Rams have fourth and inches on Minnesota's goal line in NFC title 
game.Young Knox says, "Field goal!" Vikings block it and run it back 99 1/2 
yards for a touchdown. 
</P>
<P>
 Saturday: Rams on Raider 36-yard line, fourth and one. Old Knox says, "Punt!" 
Into the end zone. Net 16 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 Goodby, Chuck; goodby, Georgia, and goodby, Rams. Good luck in (fill in city). 
Loyal since 1946, this Ram fans says, "Enough is enough." 
</P>
<P>
 BOB GRISANTI 
</P>
<P>
 San Gabriel 
</P>
