<P>
'MI VIDA LOCA' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I was reading about the movie "Mi Vida Loca" prior to Kevin Thomas' movie 
review ("The Road to 'Mi Vida Loca' Paved With Good Intentions," July 22).And I 
was poised to write. I wanted to express that the blight of society that this 
film depicts does not represent any large proportion of Latin society. 
</P>
