<HEADLINE>
<P>
NITTY-GRITTY: INSIDE & OUT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Before placing in dishwasher, put small kitchen utensils in net bags from 
produce.Items won't fall through racks. 
</P>
<P>
 * To prevent red stains on plastic storage containers, spray with vegetable 
oil before storing tomato sauces. 
</P>
<P>
 * King-size pillowcases make good covers for the pad on an infant changing 
table. 
</P>
<P>
 * Keep drain unclogged by covering it with steel wool before washing a cat or 
dog. 
</P>
<P>
 * When rolling out dough, cover countertop with a sheet of waxed paper secured 
with a few drops of water; cleanup will be simple. 
</P>
<P>
 * Water your garden thoroughly without wasting water by installing soaker 
hoses that ooze water slowly to the roots. 
</P>
