<TEXT>
<P>
 Free immunizations and checkups for children will be available at an afternoon 
health fair in Simi Valley on Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
 For the fifth straight year, Simi Valley Hospital is holding its Kids Care 
Fair for children between the ages of 2 months and 18 years. 
</P>
<P>
