Trailer Derby Challenge at 400 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 Bluyx, who defeated $20,000 claimers by a nose in his last start on Aug. 12, 
is one of four horses entered by trainer Blane Schvaneveldt. He will also be 
represented by First Gray Dawn, Le Ritz and Pecuniary Perks and the latter two 
will race as an entry. 
