<TEXT>
<P>
 San Andreas Fault -- In an Aug. 15 story about the Agua Dulce Airpark, The 
Times incorrectly reported the location of a portion of the San Andreas Fault. 
The fault runs about 12 miles north of Agua Dulce. 
</P>
